PrecisAppointment of Louis Davies Hyndman, of Edmonton, Alberta, as Chairperson and Warren E. Everson, of Ottawa, Ontario, and Johanne Gauthier, of Montreal, Quebec, as Members to carry out a comprehensive review of the operations of the Canadian Transportation Accident Investigation and Safety Board Act for the purpose of assessing its effect on the safety of air, marine, rail and commodity pipeline transportation and to complete an submit a report in both official languages to the Minister on or before January 31, 1994.
